  "detailed_description": "<h1>DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0da8cfb490b046cf14d7c429a2811c5b.poster.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0da8cfb490b046cf14d7c429a2811c5b.webm?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0da8cfb490b046cf14d7c429a2811c5b.mp4?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THIS IS NOT A GAME OF CLASSIC CHESS!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Fog of War</strong> feature hides enemy armies. <strong>Dark Chess</strong> is both about quick decisions, tactical thinking and taking risks or thinking slow and scouting the unknown before taking a step into dark. Reworked and enhanced game rules will bring immense joy to die-hard chess-lovers and casual players alike. Game keeps players thrilled with unexpected moves and unforeseen attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/090109bb36201fe689533a67adf18ae1.avif?t=1754999139\" width=610 height=239 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game-changing feature of Fog of War </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully narrated, story-driven campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet and challenge famous kings and queens</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All-new visual chess experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable avatars and profiles </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ADVENTURE TIME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/4876344926f3c9625ac6032c6743fcb7.poster.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/4876344926f3c9625ac6032c6743fcb7.webm?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/4876344926f3c9625ac6032c6743fcb7.mp4?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Take a step to walk deeper into the <strong>Dark Chess</strong> single player story campaign to fight Queens and Kings of the past. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you dare to challenge the famous <strong>Genghis Khan</strong>, outsmart <strong>King Solomon</strong> or terrify <strong>Ivan the Terrible</strong>? Dare to argue with <strong>Queen Elizabeth</strong> or <strong>Empress Cixi</strong> and keep the head on your shoulders? Be warned my friend, some of them will not play by the rules! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expect the unexpected after the first move. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/edc3d4d358ac4a2e24d7043606788e58.poster.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/edc3d4d358ac4a2e24d7043606788e58.webm?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/edc3d4d358ac4a2e24d7043606788e58.mp4?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REWARDS & CUSTOMIZATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever won a difficult chess duel feeling that you deserved a reward and got none? <strong>Dark Chess</strong> is going to reward you for your achievements! For every difficult puzzle you solve, difficult opponent you destroy or clever move you make, you'll be rewarded with an achievement that unlocks visuals improvements. You can customize in game avatar the way you want. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0bb5202fe3d7e58b96a2b5f180d8600e.poster.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0bb5202fe3d7e58b96a2b5f180d8600e.webm?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0bb5202fe3d7e58b96a2b5f180d8600e.mp4?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you are a die-hard chess lover or a board game enthusiast, <strong>Dark Chess</strong> will appeal to anyone who loves the thrill of a chess battle.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/cffc2ab1ffa5f0e3898e5aabc7502180.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=168 /></span></p>",
