ward and got none? <strong>Dark Chess</strong> is going to reward you for your achievements! For every difficult puzzle you solve, difficult opponent you destroy or clever move you make, you'll be rewarded with an achievement that unlocks visuals improvements. You can customize in game avatar the way you want. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0bb5202fe3d7e58b96a2b5f180d8600e.poster.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0bb5202fe3d7e58b96a2b5f180d8600e.webm?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0bb5202fe3d7e58b96a2b5f180d8600e.mp4?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you are a die-hard chess lover or a board game enthusiast, <strong>Dark Chess</strong> will appeal to anyone who loves the thrill of a chess battle.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/cffc2ab1ffa5f0e3898e5aabc7502180.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=168 /></span></p>",
